is-- we can only

00:02:59.880 --> 00:03:01.700
see electromagnetic
radiation that's

00:03:01.700 --> 00:03:04.167
been traveling for
13.7 billion years.

00:03:04.167 --> 00:03:05.750
In another billion
years, the universe

00:03:05.750 --> 00:03:07.139
